                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14464689" author="blackdrag" created="Thu, 24 Apr 2008 16:20:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this issue sure is puzzling.. I tried to fix it by adding several workarounds, but it seems the only thing that will be accepted after &quot;] as ThreadLocal&amp;lt;Integer&amp;gt;&quot; is the end of the class.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14464609" author="blackdrag" created="Thu, 24 Apr 2008 17:13:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ok, looks like the grammar matches the nls after &amp;gt;, meaning it fails to recognize the command end.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14464588" author="blackdrag" created="Thu, 24 Apr 2008 17:49:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;found the right nls. fixed now&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
